SmProcessing

Class V3Process

  • java.lang.Object
    • SmProcessing.V3Process

  • public class V3Process
extends java.lang.Object
    The V3Process class executes the steps necessary to generate a V3 product file from a V2 component object. It calculates the FFT of the corrected acceleration and extracts the values at the periods of interest, and calculates the spectra at each damping value.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      V3Process(V2Component v2acc, V2Process v2val)
      The constructor reads in the coefficient files and the period file and stores them for use during the calculations.

      • V3Process

        public V3Process(V2Component v2acc,
                 V2Process v2val)
          throws java.io.IOException,
                 SmException,
                 FormatException
        The constructor reads in the coefficient files and the period file and stores them for use during the calculations.
        Parameters:
        v2acc - the V2 component with corrected acceleration
        v2val - the V2 process object holding the padded acceleration array
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if unable to read in the coefficient files
        SmException - if the sampling interval in the real header is invalid
        FormatException - if unable to parse the values in the coefficient files
